Posts.Content: Hi wayne, My name is Bonnie and my husband has small cell lung cancer. I also believe in building the immune system. Can you please tell me what you tried? And tell me your story, I really need to know. Thanks, Bonnie
Posts.Title: Has Anyone Had Success With Alternative Treatments?

Posts.Content: Yes, hi I read your message. I understand that you had stage 3 lung cancer and did other options then chemo and are doing great. My husband has small cell cancer will be finishing his treatments soon. We went to a nutritionist who put him on a special diet and supplements. Would love to compare notes. Bonnie

Posts.Content: Yes I read your message. My husband has small cell cancer. He is on a special diet and supplements took him to a nutritionist. She has done woderful things. If you would like more info let me know and I will give the info I have. Bonnie
